                     <interp inst="t17870418-44-off204" type="offenceSubcategory" value="housebreaking"></interp>
               feloniously breaking and entering the dwelling house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17870418-44-victim409" type="victimName">
                           Edward 
                           Harrold
                        <interp inst="t17870418-44-victim409" type="surname" value="Harrold"></interp>
